      "content": "he's really stubborn about it and says he just needs to drink a lot of water and take a nap. if i just give him some aspirin and let him sleep for a few hours to see if he wakes up feeling more normal, would that be okay? i really don't want to cause him unnecessary stress with an ambulance if it's just travel fatigue.",
